Source: kairosos
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: KairosOS Team <dev@kairosos.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), cargo, rustc, python3, python3-pip, linux-headers-amd64
Standards-Version: 4.7.0
Homepage: https://kairosos.org
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/kairosos/kairosos
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/kairosos/kairosos.git
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: kairosos-daemons
Architecture: linux-any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libelf1, libssl3
Description: KairosOS core daemons
 Production-hardened system daemons for the KairosOS autonomous
 operating system. Includes 20 Rust daemons for BPF telemetry,
 declarative config, recovery, inference, mesh networking, and more.

Package: kairosos-mcp-servers
Architecture: linux-any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: KairosOS MCP protocol servers
 JSON-RPC 2.0 MCP servers for filesystem, process, systemd, and
 Ollama integration.

Package: kairosos-ai-services
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3, python3-asyncio
Description: KairosOS AI microservices
 Python-based AI microservices including confidence scoring, context
 management, supervision, knowledge graphs, and telemetry aggregation.

Package: kairosos-kernel-modules
Architecture: linux-any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, kmod
Description: KairosOS kernel modules
 Custom kernel modules for dm-verity, TPM, EDAC, PTP, framebuffer,
 IOMMU, and PROCHOT thermal management.

Package: kairosos-scripts
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, bash, systemd, kmod, util-linux
Description: KairosOS management scripts
 74 production-hardened shell scripts for security, network, hardware,
 storage, and self-healing system management.

Package: kairosos-full
Architecture: linux-any
Depends: kairosos-daemons, kairosos-mcp-servers, kairosos-ai-services,
         kairosos-kernel-modules, kairosos-scripts
Description: KairosOS full installation (metapackage)
 Complete KairosOS autonomous operating system suite.
